# Bootstrap toolkit repo

This repository **generates** product scaffolds. It is not a Forge integration harness and not a deployed application.

## Do

- Change `templates/new-project/`, `profiles/`, `scripts/launch_project.sh`, and bootstrap tests.
- Promote stable patterns from [Project-1](https://github.com/nicksinx/Project-1) into templates when they apply to **all** new products.
- Run `make check` before merging launcher or profile changes.
- Keep Cursor rules canonical under `templates/tool-adapters/.cursor/rules/`.

## Do not

- Vendor Forge server source into bootstrap.
- Treat bootstrap as the place for full E2E harness evidence (that lives in Project-1).
- Add product-only OKF requirements that belong in generated repos.

